@startuml US-14
title US-14 View Games by Developer

actor User
boundary "Web UI" as UI
control "DeveloperController" as DC
control "DeveloperService" as DS
database "GameRepository" as GR

User -> UI: Click developer name
UI -> DC: GET /developers/{developerId}/games
DC -> DS: listGamesByDeveloper(developerId)
DS -> GR: findByDeveloperId(developerId)
GR --> DS: games
DS --> DC: games
DC --> UI: 200 OK + list
UI --> User: Render developer's games
@enduml
